The MIT license above covers only the files originally written for this
repository: the meta-edgeos Yocto layer, the demo CLIs (edgeos-detect,
edgeos-benchmark, edgeos-perfctl), the host helper scripts under bin/, the
build configuration under build-edgeos-headless/conf/, and the documentation.

Everything else fetched by `repo sync` (poky, meta-imx, meta-openembedded,
meta-ros, etc.) keeps its own original license. The image produced by the
build bundles a lot of third-party software whose licenses have practical
consequences for redistribution. See THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md for the items
that matter.
